  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ようこそ、
いらっしゃいました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You are most welcome in my domain.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私に何の用ですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What exactly is your business?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔界の扉を閉じるために、
あなたの力を
お借りしたいのです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Luna, we need your powers once again.
The Otherwordly Gate must be closed
to prevent a monster rampage.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>One more thing...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293764</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ……あの、わたしたち、
なくした精霊晶核を
取り戻したいんですが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-Well... Our Elements' Pot broke and
I would like to ask if there's any
possibility it could be restored...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293844</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>手ぶらで
私に頼みごとですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're daring to ask this much while empty-handed?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293912</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いえ、あの……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, you see...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>294092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そのあなたたちの非礼、
正してあげます。
覚悟しなさい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How impudent! Your attitude must be
corrected this instant. Prepare yourself!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>294172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちょっ……
いきなり何だよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Woah! That escalated quickly!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>294252</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ど、どうされたのですか……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-Why are you intent on fighting us?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>294348</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうもこうもありません！
……てか、逃げるな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I've no need to explain...! You
shall not escape your sins!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>294436</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ルナって、
こんな精霊だったっけ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Luna, are you really the Summon
Spirit we met once before?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>294516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ち、違うと思うんですが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She does seem rather different...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>294580</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_020_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>くそっ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is bad...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
